; head and thorax: Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F7837016" captionText="Figure 2. Ogcogaster segmentator (Westwood, 1847), female. A head and thorax, dorsal view; B head, frontal view. Scale bar: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.10.e85742.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/673503" pageId="0" pageNumber="85742">2</figureCitation>
; wing: Fig. 
