; female genitalia: Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F7837024" captionText="Figure 4. Ogcogaster segmentator (Westwood, 1847), female, genitalia. A lateral view; B ventral view. Abbreviation: ect: ectoproct; gx: gonocoxites; gp: gonapophyses; S: sternite; T: tergite. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.10.e85742.figure4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/708522" pageId="0" pageNumber="85742">4</figureCitation>
